\[ds^2 
= - (1+2A) c^2 dt^2 - 2B_i cdt dx^i + \{(1+2D) \delta_{ij} + 2E_{ij}\} dx^i dx^j \tag{1}\]

<p>å¯¾å¿œã™ã‚‹ãƒ¡ãƒˆãƒªãƒƒã‚¯ãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚½ãƒ«ã‚’è¡Œåˆ—ã§æ›¸ãã¨</p>

\[(g_{\mu \nu}) 
= \left( \begin{array}{cccc}
-(1+2A) &amp; - B_1 &amp; -B_2 &amp; -B_3 \\
-B_1 &amp; 1 + 2D + 2 E_{11}&amp; 2E_{12} &amp; 2E_{13} \\
-B_2 &amp; 2 E_{21}&amp; 1+2D+2E_{22} &amp; 2E_{23} \\
-B_3 &amp; 2 E_{31}&amp; 2E_{32} &amp; 1+2D+2E_{33} \\
\end{array} \right) \tag{2}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§\(A\)ã‚’ãƒ©ãƒ—ã‚¹é–¢æ•°(lapse function)ã€\(B^i = (B_1, B_2, B_3)\)ã‚’ã‚·ãƒ•ãƒˆãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«(shift vector)ã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚
\(E_{ij}\)ã¯ãƒ¡ãƒˆãƒªãƒƒã‚¯ã®æ‘‚å‹•ã®ç©ºé–“æˆåˆ†ã®ãƒˆãƒ¬ãƒ¼ã‚¹ãƒ¬ã‚¹æˆåˆ†ã§ã™ã€‚
\(g_{\mu \nu}\)ã®é€†è¡Œåˆ—ã€\(g^{\mu \nu}\)ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ãã®ãŸã‚ã«ã€\(g_{\mu \nu} = \eta_{\mu \nu} + h_{\mu \nu}\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€æ‘‚å‹•éƒ¨åˆ†ã‚’\(h_{\mu \nu}\)ã¨æ›¸ãã“ã¨ã«ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;g^{\mu \nu} 
= \eta^{\mu \nu} + h^{\mu \nu} 
= g^{\mu \alpha} g^{\nu \beta} (\eta_{\alpha \beta} + h_{\alpha \beta}) 
= (\eta^{\mu \alpha} + h^{\mu \alpha}) (\eta^{\nu \beta} + h^{\nu \beta}) (\eta_{\alpha \beta} + h_{\alpha \beta}) \notag \\
\quad &amp;\simeq \eta^{\mu \nu} + 2 h^{\mu \nu} + \eta^{\mu \alpha} \eta^{\nu \beta} h_{\alpha \beta} 
= g^{\mu \nu} + h^{\mu \nu} + \eta^{\mu \alpha} \eta^{\nu \beta} h_{\alpha \beta} \notag \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \ 
h^{\mu \nu} 
= - \eta^{\mu \alpha} \eta^{\nu \beta} h_{\alpha \beta} \tag{3}
\end{align}\]

